ot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/good-character-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":1972,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character is heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier upon the scale of a believer on the Day of Resurrection than his good character. Verily, Allah hates the vulgar and obscene.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2002 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/kull-maruf-sadaqah-smiling\/","url_meta":{"origin":1972,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Every good deed is charity, even smiling","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery good deed is charity. Verily, it is a good deed to meet your brother with a smiling face, and to pour what is left from your bucket into your brother's vessel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40119,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/14\/gratitude-both\/","url_meta":{"origin":1972,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ingratitude: Be grateful to both Allah and people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is never thankful to people is never thankful to Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1955 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10093,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/01\/hilm-evil-with-evil-forgive\/","url_meta":{"origin":1972,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Patience: The Prophet does not respond to evil with evil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdullah al-Khadali reported: I ask